@node "Introduction" "Introducing....  2 small scripts"
@prev "Main"
 Nothing fancy here.  These 2 scripts do 2 things...


        1.  Click on a URL inside a YAM message, and Voyager will
            execute (if neccessary) and automatically bring up
            that URL.


        2.  Click on a MAILTO: link on a Webpage in Voyager, and
            YAM (v2.0) will execute (if neccessary) and automatically
            enter the EMail address, and the URL will be passed as the
            subject.


Requirements:
                YAM v2.0+
                Voyager-NG 2.95+
                Amiga
                18mb RAM (oops, sorry - thas was the Windows version :)
@endnode

